

French report, reported in bien.org:

"CENTRE D'ANALYSE STRATEGIQUE (2007), Les dotations en capital pour les jeunes, Paris: La Documentation française, ISBN : 978-2-11-006754-8.

 

This new report by the "Centre d'analyse stratégique" of the French government (a research centre directly attached to the Prime Minister) focuses on "capital grants", and includes references to Paine, Ackerman & Alstott, and Nissan & Le Grand. It explores three scenarios for the implementation of such grants in the French context.

The report can be downloaded at:
http://www.strategie.gouv.fr/IMG/pdf/Rapport_no9_Web.pdf


